---
title: Frozen Pizza
tags: kid-friendly, quick and easy
servings: 2
cook time: 15 minutes
ai_image: true
date added: 2026-03-17
---

Preheat oven to 425°F. Remove @Totino's Party Pizza{1} from packaging and place directly on the center oven rack. Bake until cheese is melted and crust is golden and crispy, about ~{13%minutes}. Remove from oven, let cool for ~{2%minutes}, then slice and serve.
